  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dad\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da7\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbb\u0dca \u0db8\u0d9c\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A head of the motor department is in a tender trap",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It is reported that a senior official of the Motor Transport Department's Driving License Printing Division has obtained a contract to supply 200 computers by submitting fake business certificates.",
        "Sources state that this information was revealed during an investigation based on a complaint received by the Motor Transport Department's Head Office Audit Division and that the accused officer also holds a high position in the Sri Lanka Army.",
        "It is reported that the relevant senior military officer has submitted a registered company in the name of his wife and obtained the tender for importing computers and one computer has been supplied at a price of over two lakh rupees.",
        "It is reported from the Department of Motor Transport that during the audit, the computers were imported through an unregistered company at a higher price.",
        "The Sri Lanka Army provided the driver's license printing due to complaints of corruption and irregularities in the printing of the driver's license done through the Werahera office, and even so, it is alleged that there are still more irregularities in the printing of the driver's license."
      ],
